<span id="Structure_toolbar"></span>
===结构工具栏===

* [[File:Std_Part.svg|32px]] [[Std_Part|新零件]]: 创建一个新零件，并将其设为活动对象。

* <span id="Part_Datums">[[File:Part_CoordinateSystem.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] 基准: {{Version|1.1}}</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Part_Datums pages redirect here-->

:* [[File:Part_CoordinateSystem.svg|32px]] [[Part_CoordinateSystem|坐标系]]: 创建一个可附着于其他对象的坐标系。{{Version|1.1}}

:* [[File:Part_DatumPlane.svg|32px]] [[Part_DatumPlane|基准面]]: 创建一个可附着于其他对象的基准面。 {{Version|1.1}}

:* [[File:Part_DatumLine.svg|32px]] [[Part_DatumLine|基准线]]: 创建一个可附着于其他对象的基准线。{{Version|1.1}}

:* [[File:Part_DatumPoint.svg|32px]] [[Part_DatumPoint|基准点]]: 创建一个可附着于其他对象的基准点。 {{Version|1.1}}

* [[File:Std_Group.svg|32px]] [[Std_Group|新建组]]: 创建一个新组。

* <span id="Std_LinkActions">[[File:Std_LinkMake.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] 链接操作:</span><!--Do not edit span id: the Std_LinkActions pages redirect here-->

:* [[File:Std_LinkMake.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkMake|创建链接]]: 创建链接。

:* [[File:Std_LinkMakeRelative.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkMakeRelative|创建子链接]]: 创建子对象或子件的链接。

:* [[File:Std_LinkReplace.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkReplace|替换为链接]]: 用新链接替换对象。

:* [[File:Std_LinkUnlink.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkUnlink|取消链接]]: 用所链接的对象替换链接。

:* [[File:Std_LinkImport.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkImport|导入链接]]: 导入选定的外部链接。

:* [[File:Std_LinkImportAll.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkImportAll|导入所有链接]]: 导入所有外部链接。

* [[File:Std_VarSet.svg|32px]] [[Std_VarSet|变量集]]: 创建一组属性， 可在[[Expressions|表达式]]中用作变量. {{Version|1.0}}

<span id="Additional_tools"></span>
===附加工具===

* [[File:Std_LinkMakeGroup.svg|32px]] [[Std_LinkMakeGroup|Link Group]]: Creates a group of links.

* [[Std_Expressions|Expression Actions]]:

:* [[Std_Expressions#Copy_Selected|Copy Selected]]: Copies expression data from selected objects to the Clipboard.

:* [[Std_Expressions#Copy_Active_Document|Copy Active Document]]: Copies expression data from the active document to the Clipboard.

:* [[Std_Expressions#Copy_All_Documents|Copy All Documents]]: Copies expression data from all documents to the Clipboard.

:* [[Std_Expressions#Paste|Paste]]: Pastes expression data from the Clipboard.

* [[Image:Part_SelectFilter.svg|x32px]][[Image:Toolbar_flyout_arrow_blue_background.svg|x32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter|选择过滤器]]: {{Version|1.0}}

:* [[Image:Vertex-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#Vertex_Selection|顶点选择]]: 只有顶点可被选中。

:* [[Image:Edge-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#Edge_Selection|边选择]]: 只有边可被选中。

:* [[Image:Face-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#Face_Selection|Face Selection]]: Only allows the selection of faces.

:* [[Image:Clear-selection.svg|32px]] [[Part_SelectFilter#No_Selection_Filters|No Selection Filters]]: Allows the selection of all subelements.

* [[File:Std_TreeSelectAllInstances.svg|32px]] [[Std_TreeSelectAllInstances|Select All Instances]]: Selects all instances of an object in the [[Tree_View|Tree View]].

* [[File:Std_ToggleFreeze.svg|32px]] [[Std_ToggleFreeze|Toggle Freeze]]: Toggles the freeze state of objects. {{Version|1.0}}

===Obsolete tools===

* [[File:Std_FreeCADFAQ.svg|32px]] [[Std_FreeCADFAQ|FreeCAD FAQ]]: Opens the FreeCAD FAQ wiki page. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.1}}.

* [[File:Std_FreeCADPowerUserHub.svg|32px]] [[Std_FreeCADPowerUserHub|Python scripting documentation]]: Opens the FreeCAD Power users documentation wiki page. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.1}}.

* [[File:Std_OnlineHelp.svg|32px]] [[Std_OnlineHelp|Help]]: Opens the help documentation. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.1}}.

* [[Image:Std_MeasureDistance.svg|32px]] [[Std_MeasureDistance|Measure distance]]: Creates an object to measure and display a distance. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}. Use [[Std Measure|Std Measure]] instead.

* [[Image:View_Measure_Clear_All.svg|32px]] [[View_Measure_Clear_All|Clear measurement]]: Clears [[Part_Workbench|Part]]  measurements. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}. Use [[Std Measure|Std Measure]] instead.

* [[Image:View_Measure_Toggle_All.svg|32px]] [[View_Measure_Toggle_All|Toggle measurement]]: Toggles the display of Part measurements. Not available in {{VersionPlus|1.0}}. Use [[Std Measure|Std Measure]] instead.


